    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到《夜之岛》（Isle of the Night）！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，你将收集资源、制作装备，并在一波波敌人的袭击下努力生存。白天探索岛屿并做好准备；夜晚则迎战强大的敌人。无论是单人游戏还是与好友组队，每一个选择都关乎你的生死。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制作、建造、生存</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/e8e91e4aa8939591f958c4a7b5e97916.poster.avif?t=1770238779\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/e8e91e4aa8939591f958c4a7b5e97916.webm?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/e8e91e4aa8939591f958c4a7b5e97916.mp4?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源，打造必需的工具和武器。砍树、采矿、狩猎，逐步建立你的武装。你能否存活下来，取决于你打造出的装备。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自由构建流派</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/373c1788dc6343daaa2b507aa5b74227.poster.avif?t=1770238779\" width=800 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/373c1788dc6343daaa2b507aa5b74227.webm?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/373c1788dc6343daaa2b507aa5b74227.mp4?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着经验的积累，你可以从各种随机升级和强化中进行选择。每次升级都能解锁独特技能和强力增益，打造属于你的战斗风格。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动态战斗系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/b768654b092d1ed1a80e75d442a0d302.poster.avif?t=1770238779\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/b768654b092d1ed1a80e75d442a0d302.webm?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/b768654b092d1ed1a80e75d442a0d302.mp4?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合近战与远程攻击，释放装备附带的技能，展开快节奏、充满动作感的战斗。当你准备就绪，便可挑战潜伏在岛屿深处的强大Boss，真正考验你的实力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>合作模式，共同生存</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/abad64a89107608831e8c072f7df84d1.avif?t=1770238779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras_big/abad64a89107608831e8c072f7df84d1.avif?t=1770238779 width=800 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友组队，一同分享资源、制定战术，迎战更加强大的敌人。团结协作，是生存的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
